                },
                {
                  "type": "h5",
                  "label": "Why it matters",
                  "text": "Tax-free compounding protects your returns. Over-contributing triggers penalties."
                },
                {
                  "type": "h5",
                  "label": "How to use it",
                  "text": "Automate monthly contributions; invest in diversified, low-cost ETFs; avoid day-trading."
                }
